>\n學coding同數理邏輯有關<br />\n所以學得好既人 數學一定唔會差<br />\n先有呢個結論"},{"pid":"a259eeb110318fdbd3376a53cef10f7d6404b186","tid":1490700,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"coding只係同電腦溝通既語言<br />\n<br />\n同數學關係真係唔大"},{"pid":"964b447eb29c972e7f05fbbddd32e0ee69629110","tid":1490700,"uid":275055,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"年輕人，你需要Techlead<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=TAAXwrgd1U8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTAAXwrgd1U8&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=3e7b9138\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=TAAXwrgd1U8</a>"},{"pid":"96d9abac164f40fe8dc0fc7f2f136596dde8792d","tid":1490700,"uid":310269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"學CODING唔一定數學好，最緊要係明白流程同規律。當然數學好可以幫助邏輯整理。"},{"pid":"fd0c38832e59c77e2175e5f9f6a442f2a3fafac7","tid":1490700,"uid":275055,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a259eeb110318fdbd3376a53cef10f7d6404b186","tid":1490700,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"coding只係同電腦溝通既語言<br />\n<br />\n同數學關係真係唔大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"如果你眼中嘅數學只有方程同幾何，我冇野講。<br />\nAlgorithm 同 abstraction 係寫code必要考慮嘅，直接決定你係咪個好嘅programmer；哩兩樣野同（高階）數學係分唔開。"},{"pid":"07708f515d07ab878aef4cae754aed37505bd0b8","tid":1490700,"uid":268797,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aa0ad9160332f5f19ca828881f3118bb1b551c20","tid":1490700,"uid":195265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:38:16.000Z","msg":"出嚟做左咗幾年嘢, 覺得coding 有趣, 但本身maths唔叻, 學coding會唔會好難? 作為職業會唔會好辛苦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201